0not%20on%20the%20road%20(or%20in%20the%20sky)%2C%20she%20uses%20the%20first%20hour%20or%20two%20of%20her%20morning%20to%20get%20through%20the%20less%20fun%2C%20more%20administrative%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tend%20to%20be%20up%20really%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20get%20myself%20ready%20and%20I%20get%20myself%20a%20coffee%2C%20log%20in%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20triage%20what%20came%20in%20overnight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELists%20are%20also%20a%20key%20part%20of%20her%20organization%2C%20Savage%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20keep%20a%20running%20list%20of%20my%20priorities.%20And%20I%20reset%20that%20list%20every%20week%2C%20and%20look%20at%20that%20and%20make%20sure%20that%20I'm%20spending%20my%20time%20on%20what%20those%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262b33a7d-20ad-4bb8-8955-cf3c14cf71d6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20right%20attitude%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20hiring%20young%20talent%2C%20Savage%20looks%20for%20curiosity%2C%20enthusiasm%2C%20and%20a%20genuine%20interest%20in%20the%20work%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20technical%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20really%20important%20that%20they%20have%20curiosity%20about%20the%20job%20and%20what%20it%20is%20that%20we're%20doing%20and%20why%20we're%20doing%20it.%20So%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20putting%20together%20a%20slide%2C%20but%20why%20are%20we%20pulling%20this%20slide%20together%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20only%20going%20to%20be%20successful%20at%20this%20job%20if%20you%20find%20it%20interesting%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSeeing%20people%20who%20really%20do%20want%20to%20understand%20how%20it%20all%20fits%20together%20is%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attribute%20that%20the%20most%20successful%20interns%20and%20young%20hires%20tend%20to%20share%20is%20a%20good%20outlook%20and%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAttitude%20is%20well%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20what%20makes%20somebody%20truly%20great%20at%20that%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20teach%20you%20the%20skills%20you%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0e2dbc6-b54a-4239-921a-2a4f575409da%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeizing%20opportunities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESavage%20didn't%20plan%20to%20become%20an%20expert%20in%20the%20automotive%20space.%20Not%20long%20after%20arriving%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20the%20bank%20needed%20someone%20to%20help%20lead%20Chrysler's%20restructuring%20after%20its%20bankruptcy.%20Savage%20raised%20her%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20where%20the%20opportunities%20are%20going%20to%20be.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20grab%20them%20when%20they%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20about%20a%20year%20on%20that%20deal%2C%20she%20saw%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20space%26quot%3B%20in%20auto%20coverage%20and%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20technology%20within%20the%20sector%20just%20as%20electric%20and%20autonomous%20vehicles%20were%20taking%20off.%20Aspiring%20bankers%2C%20take%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20resilient%20and%20adaptable%20and%2C%20when%20you%20see%20an%20opportunity%2C%20jumping%20at%20it%20and%20with%20both%20hands%2C%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20number%20one%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%20would%20give.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESavage%20also%20warns%20not%20to%20dwell%20on%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20could've%20been.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20point%20in%20looking%20at%20closed%20doors%20or%20other%20paths%20that%20are%20closed%20to%20you.%20I%20feel%20like%20people%20worry%20that%20they%20missed%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20waste%20calories%2C%20energy%2C%20brainpower%20on%20regret.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9522d9a-e099-4828-9b58-20067f4bfff3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20your%20superpower%3C%2Fst