ones.%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20drought-prone%20districts%20like%20Solapur%2C%20Beed%2C%20Aurangabad%2C%20and%20Parbhani%2C%20has%20seen%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20this%20variety%E2%80%94followed%20by%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F389465%2Fparmeshwar-thorat-avocado-organic-farming-drought-beed-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFarmers%20also%20praise%20its%20high%20yields%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20go%20up%20to%2010%20tonnes%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBut%20who%20developed%20the%20Golden%20Sitaphal%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20sat%20down%20with%2067-year-old%20farmer%20innovator%20Navnath%20Kaspate%2C%20the%20mind%20behind%20this%20unique%20variety.%20In%202019%2C%20his%20innovation%20earned%20him%20Intellectual%20Property%20Rights%20from%20the%20Protection%20of%20Plant%20Varieties%20and%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Rights%20Authority%20(PPV%26amp%3BRA).%20Today%2C%20he%20owns%20a%2070-acre%20farm%E2%80%94Madhuban%20Farm%20and%20Nursery%E2%80%94which%20is%20home%20to%2042%20different%20varieties%20of%20custard%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETracing%20the%20history%20of%20Golden%20Sitaphal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelonging%20to%20the%20Annonaceae%20family%2C%20custard%20apple%E2%80%94heart-shaped%2C%20spherical%2C%20or%20irregular%E2%80%94features%20quilted%20skin%20that%20turns%20brown%20as%20it%20ripens.%20Originally%20from%20South%20America%20and%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20Sitaphal%20was%20introduced%20to%20India%20by%20the%20Portuguese%20in%20the%2016th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemarkably%2C%20depictions%20of%20custard%20apples%20appear%20in%20ancient%20Indian%20sculptures%2C%20such%20as%20those%20at%20Bharhut%2C%20Sanchi%2C%20Ajanta%2C%20and%20Mathura%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%202nd%20century%20BCE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20varieties%20like%20Balanagar%2C%20Phule%20Purandhar%2C%20and%20Lal%20Sitaphal%20exist%2C%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%20is%20expanding%20rapidly%20due%20to%20its%20strong%20market%20acceptance%20and%20profitability%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStarted%20by%20one%20innovator%2C%20many%20followed%20suit%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20dryland%20crop%2C%20custard%20apple%20requires%20minimal%20irrigation%E2%80%94especially%20in%20the%20first%20two%20years%E2%80%94and%20is%20well-suited%20for%20drip%20irrigation%2C%20resulting%20in%20fewer%20pest%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470-500x375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Golden%20Sitaphal%20farmer%20innovator%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470-150x113.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470.jpg%201600w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMany%20farmers%20and%20experts%20praise%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%20for%20its%20high%20yield%2C%20larger%20fruit%20size%2C%20fewer%20seeds%2C%20and%20better%20market%20prices.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaspate%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20grow%20grapes%20and%20ber%2C%20but%20after%20developing%20NMK-01%2C%20I%20converted%20my%20entire%20farm%20to%20Sitaphal%2C%20inspiring%20others%20to%20follow.%E2%80%9D%20Farmers%20in%20five%20talukas%E2%80%94Barshi%2C%20Khamgaon%2C%20Ghormale%2C%20Kasarwadi%2C%20and%20Wanewadi%E2%80%94took%20to%20the%20charm%20of%20custard%20apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Barshi%20taluka%20alone%2C%20140%20villages%20now%20cultivate%20custard%20apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20Is%20NMK-01%20Golden%20Sitaphal%20the%20most%20preferred%20variety%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20173%20accepted%20%3Cem%3EAnnona%3C%2Fem%3E%20species%20worldwide%2C%20Kaspate%E2%80%99s%2070-acre%20Madhuban%20Farm%20and%20Nursery%20is%20like%20a%20living%20museum.%20You%20can%20find%20%3Cem%3EAnnona%20glabra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EPink%E2%80%99s%20Mammoth%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EAnnona%20muricata%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EIcecal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Jem%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EAnnona%20montana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20many%20more%20on%20his%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20farm%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20nursery%20devoted%20to%20Sitaphal%20and%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20development%20and%20research%20centre.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20hosts%20prospective%20custard%20apple%20growers%20with%20free%20full-day%20workshops%20on%20agronomic%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20created%20around%203%2C000%20varieties%20using%20the%20process%20of%20cross-pollination.%20These%20cannot%20be%20found%20elsewhere.%20Only%20when%20one%20registers%20a%20variety%20with%20an%20authority%20like%20the%20PPV%20%26amp%3B%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Rights%20Authority%20(FRA)%2C%20can%20it%20be%20officially%20recognised.%20I%20have%20selected%20some%20of%20them%2C%20filed%20for%20patents%2C%20and%20started%20acquiring%20Intellectual%20Property%20Rights%20(IPR).%20In%20India%2C%20living%20things%20like%20plants%20and%20animals%2C%20and%20the%20natural%20processes%20used%20to%20produce%20them%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20patented%E2%80%94but%20they%20can%20receive%20other%20forms%20of%20IPR%20protection%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolapur%E2%80%99s%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20highlights%20several%20of%20his%20innovative%20custard%20apple%20varieties%3A%20Annona-2%2C%20NMK-1%2C%20NMK-2%2C%20NMK-3%2C%20and%20Finger%20Prints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Kaspate%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20varieties%20is%20NMK-1%2C%20which%20he%20began%20developing%20in%202002.%20Farmers%20love%20it%20for%20its%20attractive%20colour%20and%20size%2C%20the%20good%20number%20of%20fruits%20each%20plant%20produces%2C%20and%20its%20uniform%20shape%E2%80%94making%20it%20ideal%20for%20export.%20The%20fruits%20also%20stay%20unripe%20on%20the%20plant%20for%2020%E2%80%9325%20days%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20crack%20after%20harvesting%2C%20and%20suffer%20fewer%20losses%20during%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EComparing%20varieties%3A%20market%20research%2C%20pricing%2C%20yield%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20farmer%20preference%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20leads%20custard%20apple%20production%20in%20India%2C%20with%20other%20popular%20varieties%20like%20Lal%20Sitaphal%2C%20Balanagari%2C%20and%20Phule%20Purandhar%20also%20grown%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%2055%2C000%20hectares%20of%20custard%20apple%20farms%20in%20India%2C%207%2C000%20hectares%20are%20in%20Maharashtra%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustard%20apples%20are%20traded%20daily%20in%20and%20outside%20the%20state%2C%20with%20supplies%20reaching%20markets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Pune%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Delhi.%20From%20market%20yards%20in%20Pune%20and%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20creamy%2C%20grainy-fleshed%20fruit%20is%20distributed%20to%20fruit%20stalls%20and%20malls%20in%20major%20cities%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20Balanagar%20and%20Phule%20Purandhar%2C%20NMK-01%20yields%20up%20to%2012%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20(versus%20five%20to%20six%20tonnes)%20and%20commands%20a%20higher%20price.%20However%2C%20while%20its%20appearance%20and%20sweetness%20appeal%20to%20many%2C%20some%20growers%20and%20consumers%20find%20its%20flavour%20less%20desirable%20than%20local%20varieties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20970px)%20100vw%2C%20970px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMhow-custard-apple-grower-in-his-farm_11zon-1753429465.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22970%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Golden%20Sitaphal%20farmer%20innovator%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMhow-custard-apple-grower-in-his-farm_11zon-1753429465.jpg%20970w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMhow-custard-apple-grower-in-his-farm_11zon-1753429465-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMhow-custard-apple-grower-in-his-farm_11zon-1753429465-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMhow-custard-apple-grower-in-his-farm_11zon-1753429465-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMhow-custard-apple-grower-in-his-farm_11zon-1753429465-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476010%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20leads%20custard%20apple%20production%20in%20India%2C%20with%20other%20popular%20varieties%20like%20Lal%20Sitaphal%2C%20Balanagari%2C%20and%20Phule%20Purandhar.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENMK-01%20is%20sweeter%20and%20visually%20attractive%2C%20but%20several%20people%20describe%20its%20taste%20as%20different%20or%20less%20appealing%E2%80%94possibly%20due%20to%20its%20hybrid%20origin%20with%20Atemoya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F407624%2Fkrushi-sarathi-app-for-farmers-in-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMany%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20experts%20praise%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%20for%20its%20high%20yield%2C%20larger%20fruit%20size%2C%20fewer%20seeds%2C%20and%20better%20market%20prices.%20Reports%20show%20that%20this%20variety%20can%20double%20production%20and%20significantly%20increase%20income%2C%20with%20some%20farmers%20earning%20up%20to%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20per%20hectare%20and%20market%20prices%20reaching%20Rs%20200%20to%20Rs%20300%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20years%20ago%2C%2035-year-old%20Ravi%20Dabhade%20from%20Jerai%20village%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Beed%20district%20planted%20around%206%2C000%20NMK-01%20custard%20apple%20saplings%20across%2012%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEncouraged%20by%20the%20success%2C%20he%20expanded%20cultivation%20by%20another%20four%20acres%20a%20few%20years%20later.%20Today%2C%20his%20orchard%20spans%20nearly%2020%20acres%2C%20yielding%20an%20impressive%20seven%20tonnes%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-500x667.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Golden%20Sitaphal%20farmer%20innovator%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459-150x200.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FKaspate-in-his-nursery-with-a-custard-apple-sapling_11zon-1753429459.jpg%201149w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476009%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKaspate%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20grow%20grapes%20and%20ber%2C%20but%20after%20developing%20NMK-01%2C%20I%20converted%20my%20entire%20farm%20to%20Sitaphal%2C%20inspiring%20others%20to%20follow.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavi%20attributes%20his%20high%20productivity%20to%20disciplined%20crop%20management%2C%20especially%20eight%20annual%20foliar%20sprays%20that%20keep%20pests%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%202018%2C%2055-year-old%20Dinesh%20Patidar%20from%20Jamli%20village%20in%20Mhow%20Cantonment%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20planted%204%2C800%20saplings%20sourced%20from%20Madhuban%20across%2012%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grow%20a%20mix%20of%20fruits%20like%20mango%2C%20dragon%20fruit%2C%20guava%2C%20and%20avocado.%20Sitaphal%20starts%20bearing%20fruit%20in%20October%2C%20and%20the%20harvest%20continues%20through%20mid-January.%20I%20typically%20get%20four%20to%20five%20tonnes%20per%20acre%2C%20bringing%20in%20a%20profit%20of%20around%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20per%20acre%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENew%20varieties%20and%20the%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaspate%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20taken%20me%20close%20to%2012%20years%20to%20develop%20the%20new%20varieties%E2%80%94NMK%20Arvi%20and%20NMK%20Samruddhi.%20Arvi%20is%20a%20cross%20between%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%20and%20Lal%20Sitaphal%2C%20while%20the%20red-coloured%20Samruddhi%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20Sitaphal%20and%20Ramphal%20(%3Cem%3EAnnona%20reticulata%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Both%20are%20harvested%20in%20February.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20December%202021%2C%20NMK%20Samruddhi%20has%20been%20tested%20over%20six%20harvests.%20On%20average%2C%20each%20fruit%20weighed%20350%20grams%2C%20had%2060%25%20pulp%2C%20and%20a%20sweetness%20level%20(Brix)%20of%2025%E2%80%94making%20it%20a%20favourite%20among%20both%20farmers%20and%20buyers.%20NMK%20Arvi%20also%20showed%20similar%20results%2C%20with%20350-gram%20fruits%2C%2055%25%20pulp%2C%20fewer%20seeds%2C%20and%20the%20same%20sweetness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaspate%20has%20distributed%20saplings%20for%20trials%20to%20farmers%20in%20Ghormale%20and%20Barshi%20talukas%20and%20plans%20to%20launch%20the%20new%20varieties%20once%20he%20secures%20IPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20submitted%20the%20documents%20about%20the%20newly%20developed%20varieties%20to%20PPV%26amp%3BRA%20in%20November%202023.%20I%20will%20introduce%20them%20to%20farmers%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20challenge%20of%20counterfeiting%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20on%20new%20varieties%2C%20Kaspate%20continues%20to%20battle%20counterfeiters%E2%80%94a%20major%20challenge%20for%20farmer-innovators%20in%20India.%20Many%20nurseries%20sell%20unauthorised%20saplings%20under%20different%20names%20to%20hide%20their%20origin%2C%20but%20they%20are%20all%20NMK-01%20(Golden)%2C%20for%20which%20Kaspate%20holds%20the%20IPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20filed%20cases%20in%20the%20Solapur%20District%20Court%20against%20220%20nurseries%20for%20selling%20counterfeits%20and%20has%20paid%20Rs%2015%20lakhs%20in%20stamp%20duty%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20every%20breakthrough%2C%20Kaspate%20not%20only%20uplifts%20his%20community%20but%20redefines%20what%20it%20means%20to%20farm%20with%20purpose%20in%20dryland%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Hiren%20Bose%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753450921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FNMK-Arvi_11zon-1753429470.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D475953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Navnath%20Kaspate%E2%80%99s%20breakthrough%20custard%20apple%20varieties%20are%20transforming%20drought-prone%20farming%2C%20doubling%20yields%2C%20and%20inspiring%20thousands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hiren%20Kumar%20Bose%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waze's%20cofounder%20said%20AI%20will%20increase%20the%20demand%20for%20software%20engineers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Uri%20Levine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68828a483d5881a51c1df409%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUri%20Levine%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20productivity%20gains%20will%20lead%20to%20higher%20demand%20for%20engineers.%3Cp%3EJemal%20Countess%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Anti-Defamation%20League%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWaze%20cofounder%20Uri%20Levine%20said%20demand%20for%20engineers%20will%20grow%20as%20AI%20tools%20increase%20productivity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20coding%20is%20still%20important%2C%20but%20adaptability%20is%20a%20key%20skill%20for%20today's%20tech%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELevine%20added%20that%20workers%20must%20use%20common%20sense%20and%20be%20okay%20with%20making%20mistakes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaze-cofounder-next-generation-will-not-drive-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWaze%20cofounder%20Uri%20Levine%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20worried%20about%20software%20engineers%20going%20extinct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20actually%20need%20even%20more%20engineers%20to%20leverage%20on%20the%20next%20generations%20in%20productivity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20serial%20entrepreneur%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevine's%20theory%20about%20the%20future%20of%20engineers%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-code-meta-microsoft-google-llamacon-engineers-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech%20companies%20are%20boasting%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20their%20use%20of%20AI%20tools%20to%20generate%20code%2C%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20job%20for%20entry-level%20workers%20in%20the%20field.%20Amid%20a%20growing%20sense%20of%20instability%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20some%20job%20seekers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineer-offers-thousands-job-referral-linkedin-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20offering%20large%20sums%20of%20money%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20those%20who%20help%20them%20land%20a%20role%2C%20while%20others%20pursue%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-science-major-panic-masters-degree-graduate-school-job-market-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bpanic%26quot%3B%20Master's%20programs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20lieu%20of%20finding%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevine%20said%20that%20if%20some%20companies%20are%20holding%20off%20on%20hiring%20engineers%20at%20the%20moment%20or%20scaling%20back%20engineering%20teams%2C%20it%20may%20be%20because%20they%20don't%20have%20an%20immediate%20need%20for%20those%20roles%20or%20haven't%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20leverage%20them.%20In%20time%20though%2C%20Levine%20said%20companies%20will%20likely%20start%20hiring%20engineers%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20stance%20on%20engineering%20echoes%20that%20of%20Okta%20CEO%20Todd%20McKinnon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fokta-ceo-software-engineer-job-market-future-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewho%20previously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20will%20be%20more%20software%20engineers%20in%20five%20years%20than%20there%20are%20today.%20McKinnon%3Cspan%3E%20said%20that%20software%20engineers'%20jobs%20have%20evolved%20before%2C%20and%20that%20demand%20for%20the%20role%20has%20always%20increased%20as%20technology%20develops.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Okta%20CEO%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Binfinite%20demand%20for%20automation%26quot%3B%20and%20tools%20that%20enhance%20productivity%20will%20lead%20to%20higher%20demand%20for%20workers.%20Levine%20similarly%20said%20that%20increased%20productivity%20will%20lead%20to%20increased%20demand%20for%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dabb5be6-d1ae-4594-9d57-62b8ac2cb9eb%5C%22%3EPrioritizing%20different%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Levine%20doesn't%20think%20AI%20will%20replace%20software%20engineers%2C%20he%20said%20AI%20may%20reshape%20jobs.%20In%20previous%20eras%20of%20technological%20revolution%20though%2C%20the%20workforce%20has%20managed%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20leverage%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-research-head-career-advice-learn-to-code-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecoding%20is%20still%20an%20important%20skill%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20for%20those%20wanting%20to%20enter%20the%20tech%20space%2C%20Levine%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bway%20less%26quot%3B%20important%20than%20it%20used%20to%20be.%20The%20key%20for%20engineers%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20workers%20in%20general%20is%20%26quot%3Badaptability%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20important%20learning%20today%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20adapt%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20world%20is%20changing%20more%20rapidly%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdaptability%20also%20means%20being%20willing%20to%20make%20mistakes.%20The%20more%20mistakes%20you%20make%2C%20the%20more%20you%20grow%20and%20build%20resilience%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20regard%20to%20choosing%20the%20right%20major%2C%20Levine%2C%20who%20teaches%20a%20university%20entrepreneurship%20class%20in%20Madrid%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20replaces%20common%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnd%20of%20the%20day%2C%20use%20your%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Levine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fembed.typeform.com%2Fnext%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-tf-live%3D%5C%2201K0FDNEGB0EC39EGFYGJYGQ07%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20software%20engineer%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaaltchek%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eaaltchek%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20aalt.19.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaze-cofounder-ai-productivity-engineers-demand-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22