%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b161bd43bb77284ba045a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPublicis%20Groupe%20CEO%20Arthur%20Sadoun%20presenting%20at%20the%20advertising%20group's%20CoreAI%20launch%20presentation.%3Cp%3EPublicis%20Groupe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20five%20advertising%20and%20M%26amp%3BA%20insiders%2C%20who%20shared%20their%20predictions%20on%20what%20Publicis%20could%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20were%20a%20few%20themes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-adtech-startups-2023-11%23gray-swan-systems-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20expertise%20in%20creating%20agents%20to%20handle%20the%20workflow%20of%20marketing%20campaigns%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompanies%20that%20use%20AI%20to%20transform%20big%20data%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-brands-using-ai-boost-marketing-delta-unilever-mars-2025-3%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euseful%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOther%20technologies%20that%20improve%20the%20efficiency%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20agency%20disciplines%2C%20such%20as%20content%20production%20or%20strategy%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20named%20some%20particular%20marketing-focused%20AI%20startups%20they%20think%20could%20be%20on%20Publicis'%20radar.%20(This%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20Publicis%20is%20in%20conversations%20with%20these%20startups.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Publicis%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8a1fab5-6797-4c6c-a58e-cd98c11f8c7c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI-powered%20ads%20could%20come%20from%20Persado%20or%20Superscale%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrands%20ranging%20from%20Toys%20%26quot%3BR%26quot%3B%20Us%20and%20Coca-Cola%20to%20Kalshi%20have%20used%20AI%20to%20create%20TV%20ads%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-has-marketing-problem-people-dont-like-hearing-about-it-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20mixed%20consumer%3C%2Fa%3E%20responses.%20But%20generative%20AI%20tech%20has%20been%20constantly%20improving%2C%20helping%20to%20reduce%20the%20time%20and%20costs%20involved%20in%20creating%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarsten%20Weide%2C%20principal%20and%20chief%20analyst%20of%20W%20Media%20Research%2C%20said%20%3Cstrong%3EPersado%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20might%20interest%20Publicis.%20The%20company%20automates%20the%20production%20of%20marketing%20messaging%20based%20on%20emotional%20triggers%20and%20other%20data.%20Founded%20in%20New%20York%20in%202012%2C%20Persado%20has%20raised%20%2486%20million%20in%20funding%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeide%20said%20Persado's%20tech%20could%20be%20combined%20with%20Publicis'%20Epsilon%20data%20arm%20to%20help%20it%20create%20more%20personalized%20and%20persuasive%20marketing%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersado%20president%20Assaf%20Baciu%20said%20that%20while%20advertising%20companies%20would%20be%20wise%20to%20seek%20out%20AI%20solutions%20as%20a%20point%20of%20differentiation%2C%20the%20company%20has%20expanded%20its%20capabilities%20beyond%20the%20advertising%20sector%20into%20areas%20such%20as%20financial%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Superscale%20Patrick%20Haede%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6883588f85e81483682ea8d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatrick%20Haede%2C%20Superscale%20cofounder%3Cp%3EMartin%20Flindt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%2C%20%3Cstrong%3ESuperscale.AI%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecould%20be%20an%20interesting%20fit%20for%20Publicis%2C%20said%20Andrew%20Buckman%2C%20chief%20growth%20officer%20of%20the%20adtech%20company%20Azerion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20pitches%20itself%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3BAI%20CMO.%26quot%3B%20It%20allows%20brands%20to%20enter%20the%20URL%20for%20the%20product%20they%20want%20to%20sell%20and%20then%20can%20almost%20instantly%20generate%20a%20campaign%20for%20TikTok%20or%20Instagram%20using%20a%20library%20of%20realistic%20AI-generated%20actors%20and%20characters.%20SuperscaleAI%20raised%20a%20%245%20million%20pre-seed%20funding%20round%20in%20June%2C%20led%20by%20the%20VC%20firm%20Creandum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuperscale.AI%20cofounder%20Patrick%20Haede%20said%20that%20while%20the%20company%20was%20not%20considering%20being%20acquired%2C%20he%20understood%20why%20it%20might%20be%20identified%20as%20a%20potential%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20capabilities%20will%20fundamentally%20transform%20advertising%20in%20every%20possible%20way%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20content%20generation%2C%20in%20which%20we%20are%20building%20a%20leading%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Haede%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afcdf8b1-70f1-42e6-bbb6-a51b1a0c5c8a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20agents%20built%20by%20Newton%20Research%20or%20Akkio%20could%20be%20of%20interest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20has%20said%20that%202025%20will%20be%20the%20year%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-evolution-software-companies-develop-ai-agents-workforce-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bjoin%26quot%3B%20the%20workforce%2C%20as%20companies%20embrace%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-internet-dark-google-openai-anthropic-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrend%3C%2Fa%3E.%20AI%20agents%20generally%20refer%20to%20virtual%20assistants%20that%20can%20complete%20tasks%20autonomously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20are%20betting%20that%20AI%20agents%20will%20be%20big%20in%20the%20advertising%20space%2C%20too.%20Ana%20Milicevic%2C%20principal%20of%20the%20digital%20consultancy%20Sparrow%20Digital%20Holdings%2C%20said%20%3Cstrong%3ENewton%20Research%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20%26quot%3Balready%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20headway%20with%20agencies.%26quot%3B%20It%20creates%20AI%20agents%20to%20handle%20data%20science%20projects%20and%20also%20works%20with%20brands%20and%20publishers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewton%20Research's%20founder%20and%20CEO%2C%20John%20Hoctor%2C%20was%20behind%20the%20media-measurement%20company%20Data%20Plus%20Math%2C%20which%20was%20sold%20to%20the%20publicly%20listed%20data%20company%20LiveRamp%20in%202019.%20Founded%20in%202023%2C%20Newton%20Research%20has%20raised%20around%20%2413%20million%20to%20date%2C%20according%20to%20PitchBook.%20Newton%20Research%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMilicevic%20also%20said%20%3Cstrong%3EAkkio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20creates%20AI%20agents%20to%20help%20media%20agencies%20better%20understand%20their%20data%2C%20might%20be%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20Publicis.%20Founded%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Cambridge%2C%20Massachusetts-based%20company%20has%20raised%20around%20%2418%20million%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJon%20Reilly%2C%20Akkio's%20cofounder%20and%20COO%2C%20said%20the%20company%20is%20building%20an%20operating%20system%20that%20automates%20%26quot%3Bgrunt%20work%26quot%3B%20so%20agencies%20can%20win%20pitches%2C%20safeguard%20margins%2C%20and%20stay%20focused%20on%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgencies%20urgently%20need%20a%20next-generation%20AI%20operating%20layer%20to%20modernize%20their%20fragmented%20stacks%2C%26quot%3B%20Reilly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20generally%20about%20the%20AI%20space%20and%20without%20naming%20specific%20startups%2C%20Eric%20Franci%20of%20the%20VC%20firm%20Aperiam%20said%20companies%20that%20create%20agentic%20tools%20for%20marketing%20workflow%20would%20be%20the%20category%20to%20watch%20for%20M%26amp%3BA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20imagines%20a%20scenario%20where%20AI%20agents%20could%20drive%20processes%20like%20ad%20optimization%2C%20campaign%20planning%2C%20and%20measurement.%20The%20result%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfaster%20turnarounds%2C%20better%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20teams%20that%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bhigher%20value%2C%20client-success%20oriented%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e33f26ad-ca11-40ef-867b-1a29682163df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20optimization%20and%20modelling%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Cassandra%20or%20Prescient%20AI%20could%20provide%20value%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAd%20optimization%20used%20to%20involve%20humans%20watching%20ad%20campaigns%20like%20hawks%2C%20and%20adjusting%20spend%2C%20targeting%2C%20and%20creative%20messaging%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20ads%20were%20performing.%20AI%20could%20automate%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Bhands-on-keyboards%26quot%3B%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeide%20said%20%3Cstrong%3EPrescient%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20an%20ad%20optimization%20platform%20that%20predicts%20the%20return%20on%20ad%20spend%20for%20e-commerce%20ads%2C%20could%20be%20an%20acquisition%20target%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Publicis.%20Miami-based%20Prescient%20has%20raised%20%2420.9%20million%20in%20funding%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20exciting%20to%20be%20mentioned%20in%20such%20a%20critical%20area%20of%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapplovin-ceo-adam-foroughi-bid-tiktok-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrescient%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Mike%20True%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20minds%20in%20the%20field%2C%20we're%20now%20focused%20on%20advancing%20the%20technology%20we%20believe%20will%20define%20the%20future%20of%20compound%2C%20intelligent%20measurement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cassandra%20cofounders%2C%20Cristian%20Nozzi%20and%20Gabriele%20Franco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%