%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFatima%20Boolani%2C%2038%2C%20is%20a%20managing%20director%20of%20software%20equity%20research%20at%20Citi%2C%20where%20she%20also%20serves%20as%20cohead%20of%20the%20company's%20US%20software%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20also%20a%20mom%20of%20two%2C%20so%20she%20wakes%20up%20between%206%20a.m.%20and%207%20a.m.%20each%20day%20to%20check%20work%20emails%2C%20news%2C%20research%20reports%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20priority%20is%20to%20get%20a%20head%20start%20on%20the%20day%20such%20that%2C%20while%20I'm%20shifting%20gears%20momentarily%20for%20personal%20and%20family%20reasons%2C%20I%20have%20a%20solid%20footing%20before%20I%20jump%20back%20into%20work%20around%208%20a.m.%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Boolani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20drink%20of%20choice%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhot%2C%20strong%20cup%20of%20coffee%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Larabars%20are%20her%20go-to%20morning%20snack%20before%20breakfast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20exercise%20is%20a%20key%20ingredient%20to%20her%20success%2C%20Boolani%20said%20she%20prefers%20midday%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20her%2C%20mornings%20are%20about%20using%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20time%20to%20her%20advantage%20and%20%26quot%3Bfilling%20that%20space%20and%20time%20with%20more%20intention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20think%20waking%20up%20at%206%20a.m.%20was%20so%20early%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%2C%20how%20much%20power%20can%20be%20packed%20in%20that%20punch%20of%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20with%20two%20children%20%E2%80%94%20is%20really%20awesome.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20CEO%20of%20a%20beauty%20brand%20tests%20her%20new%20products%20while%20working%20out%20each%20morning.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20in%20a%20backpack%20and%20hiking%20clothes%20on%20a%20high%20hilltop%20looking%20over%20a%20sunny%20landscape%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a9845843bb77284b9e3e6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERucking%20is%20a%20fancy%20word%20for%20carrying%20a%20backpack%20as%20exercise%2C%20whether%20your%20in%20a%20beautiful%20landscape%20or%20just%20walking%20around%20your%20neighborhood.%3Cp%3EOlga%20Pankova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-urban-decay-cofounder-wende-zomnir-created-beauty-empire-caliray-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWende%20Zomnir%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2057%2C%20has%20spent%20decades%20in%20the%20beauty%20industry.%20She%20co-founded%20Urban%20Decay%20in%201996%2C%20led%20the%20brand%20until%202022%2C%20and%20then%20launched%20her%20beauty%20line%20Caliray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%20in%20her%20career%2C%20she%20wakes%20up%20between%205%20a.m.%20and%206%20a.m.%20each%20day%20and%20instantly%20drinks%2020%20ounces%20of%20water.%20Her%20second%20morning%20drink%20is%20coffee%20or%20coconut%20water%20with%20some%20protein%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20chooses%20the%20latter%20on%20days%20that%20she%20exercises%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vital%20aspects%20of%20her%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lift%2C%20practice%20yoga%2C%20play%20tennis%2C%20or%20go%20rucking%20in%20the%20soft%20sand%20most%20mornings%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20playing%20beach%20volleyball%2C%20surfing%2C%20snowboarding%2C%20riding%20my%20bike%20%E2%80%94%20I%20like%20to%20move!%20And%20I%20test%20out%20makeup%20formulas%20I'm%20working%20on%20while%20I%20do%20it%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZomnir%20said%20waking%20up%20early%20and%20jumping%20into%20physical%20activities%20helps%20her%20focus%20on%20her%20role%20as%20CEO%20and%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20thinking%20about%20when%20I'm%20going%20to%20squeeze%20my%20workout%20in%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BPhysical%20activity%20is%20my%20drug%20of%20choice%2C%20so%20I%20work%20better%20when%20I've%20worked%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20my%20kids%20got%20older%2C%20they%20needed%20me%20less%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20so%20I%20was%20able%20to%20shift%20from%20afternoon%20workouts%20to%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BMaking%20adjustments%20that%20sync%20with%20the%20life%20stages%20of%20my%20family%20and%20being%20willing%20to%20optimize%20my%20routine%20has%20made%20the%20biggest%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20fintech%20communications%20CEO%20says%20dance%20breaks%20are%20essential.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224263%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mom%20dances%20with%20two%20kids%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687f914d85e81483682e6c72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223197%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKNSY%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGrace%20Keith%20Rodriguez%2C%2040%2C%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Caliber%20Corporate%20Advisers%2C%20a%20fintech%20communications%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20gets%20the%20most%20done%20when%20she%20wakes%20up%20around%205%3A30%20a.m.%20That%20gives%20her%20time%20to%20shower%2C%20get%20dressed%2C%20brew%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20(from%20Little%20Seed%20Coffee%20Roasters%2C%20a%20company%20founded%20by%20her%20sister%20and%20brother-in-law)%2C%20and%20read%20the%20news%20from%20her%20front%20porch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20she%20can%20enjoy%20one%20of%20the%20most%20special%20parts%20of%20her%20mornings%3A%20a%20dance%20party%20with%20her%20two%20children.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shakes%20the%20sillies%20out%20and%20gets%20you%20through%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20cold%20plunge%2C%20but%20it%20sort%20of%20has%20the%20same%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeith%20Rodriguez's%20job%20also%20invo