%E2%80%98just%20transition%20roadmaps%E2%80%99%20to%20ensure%20binding%20commitments%20and%20alignment%20with%20central%20energy%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Early%20reskilling%20and%20workforce%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20district-level%20workforce%20mapping%20in%20coal%20regions%2C%20including%20formal%2C%20informal%2C%20and%20dependent%20populations%2C%20should%20be%20conducted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20workforce%20in%20the%20coal%20sector%20is%20not%20affected%20by%20the%20transition.%20The%20targeted%20reskilling%20for%20jobs%20in%20solar%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%2C%20energy%20efficiency%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20should%20be%20initiated%20at%20least%202%E2%80%933%20years%20before%20the%20projected%20mine%20or%20plant%20decommissioning%2C%20using%20the%20Skill%20Council%20for%20Green%20Jobs%20(SCGJ)%E2%80%93aligned%20curriculum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reskilling%20coal%20sector%20workers%20for%20solar%2C%20EVs%2C%20and%20green%20hydrogen%20is%20key%20to%20a%20just%20transition.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753409739-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-ima