%2Fhow-to-grow-water-lily-at-home-gardener-viji-abi-shares-easy-tips-thrissur-nymphaea-sree%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20lillies%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0at%20home%2C%20Lathika%20attended%20numerous%20workshops%20and%20classes%20conducted%20by%20the%20agricultural%20department%20in%20the%20district.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20took%20help%20from%20other%20people%20who%20are%20into%20lotus%20cultivation.%20Then%2C%20I%20started%20experimenting%20myself%20and%20learnt%20during%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20on%20her%20experience%20and%20knowledge%20gained%20from%20workshops%2C%20classes%2C%20and%20interactions%20with%20industry%20experts%2C%20Lathika%20eventually%20honed%20her%20skills%20in%20growing%20these%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGrowing%20hundreds%20of%20lotus%20%26amp%3B%20lilies%20effortlessly%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELathika%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20approach%20to%20plant%20care%20sets%20her%20apart.%20She%20advocates%20for%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354271%2Fhow-to-make-organic-natural-fertiliser-biofertiliser-easy-recipe-watermelon-cow-dung-urban-home-gardener%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse%20of%20natural%20fertilisers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20her%20home%20garden%2C%20she%20uses%20dried%20cow%20dung%2C%20used%20tea%20leaves%2C%20powdered%20eggshells%2C%20and%20sometimes%20DAP%20(di-ammonium%20phosphate)%20to%20nurture%20her%20botanical%20treasures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20sunlight%2C%20water%2C%20and%20quality%20soil%20over%20chemical%20fertilisers%2C%20she%20demonstrates%20the%20simplicity%20and%20ease%20of%20managing%20lotuses%20and%20water%20lilies%2C%20making%20them%20accessible%20even%20to%20amateur%20gardeners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20her%20impressive%20collection%20of%20lotus%20and%20water%20lilies%2C%20she%20also%20grows%20orchids%2C%20begon