t%20least%20three%20years%20to%20switch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20three%20years%2C%20a%20lot%20can%20happen%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20realisation%20shifted%20her%20focus.%20If%20industries%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20move%2C%20she%20would%20start%20with%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20method%20to%20the%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESushmita%20knew%20the%20method%20would%20only%20matter%20if%20people%20could%20use%20it.%20So%20she%20began%20conducting%20hands-on%20workshops%2C%20sharing%20her%20process%20with%20students%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20women%20from%20local%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20I%E2%80%99ve%20started%20training%20people%20to%20make%20paper%20from%20water%20hyacinth.%20Many%20colleges%20are%20interested%20in%20adapting%20it%20for%20their%20own%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20National%20College%2C%20Trichy%2C%20she%20ran%20a%20two-day%20workshop%20that%20combined%20science%20with%20skill-building.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20theory%20session%20on%20the%20first%20day%20about%20water%20hyacinths%2C%20but%20the%20second%20day%20we%20had%20hands-on%20experience%20in%20creating%20the%20papers%20from%20scratch%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ishika%2C%20a%20student%20who%20attended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-media-text__media%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-500x664.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10_11zon-1753267842-500x664.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSushmita-Krishnan-10